Privacy Policy for Smart Switch - Data Transfer App
Thank you for using the Smart Switch - Data Transfer App, created by Nova Apps Studios. This Privacy Policy outlines how your personal information is collected, used, and protected when you use our app.
Information We Collect
1. Personal Information:
In the new cloud storage feature user will have to create the account using their Google account to backup their data on the cloud.
The App does not collect any personally identifiable information from users.
2. Usage Data:
We may collect non-personal information about how the App is accessed and used. This may include device information and usage statistics.
Permissions
The App may request the following permissions:
1. Storage Access:
Required for saving transferred data on your device.
2. Network Access:
Necessary for transferring data between devices via network connectivity.
3. Camera/Media Access:
Required for accessing photos and media files for transfer.
4. Device ID:
Only accessed if required for specific features, such as identifying devices for seamless transfer.
How We Use Your Information
We use the collected information for the following purposes:
To improve the functionality and performance of the App.
To analyze usage patterns and optimize user experience.
Data Security
We prioritize the security of your information and implement appropriate measures to protect it.
Third-Party Services
The App may contain links to third-party websites or services. We have no control over the content or privacy policies of these third-party services and are not responsible for their practices.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page, and the effective date will be updated accordingly. Users are encouraged to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy or the App's permissions, please contact us at novappstudiofeedback@gmail.com.
By using the Smart Switch - Data Transfer App, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.
